Package me.vivian.displayer

Class SubCommandExecutor

java.lang.Object
me.vivian.displayer.SubCommandExecutor
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.bukkit.command.TabCompleter
public class SubCommandExecutor extends Object implements org.bukkit.command.TabCompleter
Tab completer for handling subcommands and their arguments in a plugin. This class reads subcommand information from the plugin's description file (plugin.yml) and provides tab completions for subcommands and their associated arguments.
